org.hl7.fhir.instance.model

Class Condition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Base
      • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.BaseResource
        • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Resource
          • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.DomainResource
            • org.hl7.fhir.instance.model.Condition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IAnyResource, IBase, IBaseHasExtensions, IBaseHasModifierExtensions, IBaseResource, IDomainResource

    public class Condition
extends DomainResource
    Use to record detailed information about conditions, problems or diagnoses recognized by a clinician. There are many uses including: recording a Diagnosis during an Encounter; populating a problem List or a Summary Statement, such as a Discharge Summary.
